<html>
<h1> Clear Page Transitions </h1> 


<ul>1. In the Pages panel, select the spread from which you want to clear the transition.
    <li>Choose None from the Transition menu in the Page Transition panel.</li>
</ul>
<ul>2. To remove transitions from all spreads, choose Clear All from the Page Transitions menu. </ul> 
</html 
